## 4. ECHO (The Broadcaster)
**Mission**: Distribute & Amplify.

| Task / Capability | Context Field (Target) | Data Type |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Input Ingestion** | `agents.ECHO.config.inputs.final_package` | [CalliopeOutput](file:///C:/Users/daria/.gemini/AXON/scratch/AXON-boilerplate/src/types/agent_types.ts#93-128) (Post-Argus) |
