## 5. SYSTEM GLOBAL CONTEXT
**Mission**: Orchestration.

| Task / Capability | Context Field (Target) | Data Type |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Agent Status Tracking** | `agents.[ID].status` | [AgentStatus](file:///C:/Users/daria/.gemini/AXON/scratch/AXON-boilerplate/src/types/system.ts#2-3) |
